
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Artist Signup App</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0f1115;
      --card: #171a21;
      --card-2: #1f2430;
      --text: #f4f7fb;
      --muted: #a9b3c4;
      --line: #2a3140;
      --accent: #3dd6a0;
      --accent-dark: #22b985;
      --danger: #ff6b6b;
      --shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
      --radius: 22px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(61,214,160,0.18), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #0b0d12 0%, #121723 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 24px 16px;
    }

    .phone-shell {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 420px;
    }

    .app-card {
      background: rgba(23, 26, 33, 0.92);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-radius: 30px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .top {
      padding: 20px 20px 8px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .logo-wrap {
      padding: 10px 20px 0;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .logo {
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #7cf0ca);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      color: #08110d;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 18px;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .brand h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      line-height: 1.05;
    }

    .brand p {
      margin: 4px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(61,214,160,0.14), rgba(61,214,160,0.05));
      border: 1px solid rgba(61,214,160,0.16);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .hero h2 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .hero p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    form {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .field {
      display: grid;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    label {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #dce4f2;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    input, select, textarea {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--card-2);
      color: var(--text);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 16px;
      font-size: 16px;
      outline: none;
    }

    input::placeholder, textarea::placeholder {
      color: #7f8a9c;
    }

    input:focus, select:focus, textarea:focus {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(61,214,160,0.16);
    }

    .helper {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.45;
      margin-top: -2px;
    }

    button {
      border: none;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-dark));
      color: #07110d;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 800;
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 16px;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    button:active {
      transform: scale(0.99);
    }

    .foot {
      margin-top: 16px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .success {
      display: none;
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(61,214,160,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(61,214,160,0.22);
      color: #dcfff2;
    }

    .success h3 {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .success p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #cbeee3;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .mini-note {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="phone-shell">
    <section class="app-card">
      <div class="top">
        <span>Artist community beta</span>
        <span>iPhone-ready</span>
      </div>

      <div class="logo-wrap">
        <div class="logo">A</div>
        <div class="brand">
          <h1>Artist Alley</h1>
          <p>Share music. Get feedback. Build together.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="hero">
          <h2>Join the early artist network.</h2>
          <p>
            A simple space for artists to connect, swap track reviews, and sharpen their sound
            without the usual fake-industry nonsense.
          </p>
        </div>

        <form id="signupForm">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="artistName">Artist name</label>
            <input id="artistName" name="artistName" type="text" placeholder="Your artist name" required />
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="email">Email</label>
            <input id="email" name="email" type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required />
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="genre">Main genre</label>
            <select id="genre" name="genre" required>
              <option value="">Choose your lane</option>
              <option>Hip-Hop / Rap</option>
              <option>R&B</option>
              <option>Pop</option>
              <option>Rock</option>
              <option>Electronic</option>
              <option>Alternative</option>
              <option>Gospel</option>
              <option>Other</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="goal">What do you want help with?</label>
            <textarea id="goal" name="goal" rows="4" placeholder="Track reviews, networking, collaboration, development..." required></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="helper">
            This first version is a simple signup page so you can start building interest fast.
          </div>

          <button type="submit">Join early access</button>
        </form>

        <div class="success" id="successMessage">
          <h3>You’re in.</h3>
          <p>
            Your early-access request has been captured in this prototype. Next step is connecting
            the form to a real database or email tool.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="foot">
          Built as a mobile web MVP for artists who want real feedback, real growth, and less fluff.
        </p>

        <p class="mini-note">
          Version 1 = signup. Version 2 = profiles, tracks, and review threads.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script>
    const form = document.getElementById('signupForm');
    const successMessage = document.getElementById('successMessage');

    form.addEventListener('submit', function (e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      successMessage.style.display = 'block';
      form.reset();
      successMessage.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'nearest' });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
